# Cursor Rules for Aurora N&N Business Solutions

## Project Overview
This is a Next.js website for Aurora N&N Business Solutions Inc., providing professional taxation services and modern web design.

## Firebase MCP Server Configuration
The Firebase MCP server is configured to provide AI assistance with Firebase development tasks.

## Code Style Guidelines
- Use TypeScript for all new code
- Follow Next.js 15+ best practices
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Implement proper error handling
- Use Firebase for backend services

## Firebase Integration
- Authentication: Firebase Auth
- Database: Firestore
- Storage: Firebase Storage
- Use the utility functions in `src/lib/firebase-utils.ts`

## File Structure
- Components in `src/components/`
- Pages in `src/app/`
- Utilities in `src/lib/`
- Firebase config in `src/lib/firebase.ts`

## Environment Variables
Required Firebase environment variables are defined in `env.example`
